{"tid":404919,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 諗住diy望遠鏡","createTime":"2017-09-18T12:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T14:18:43.000Z","uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f16600e4010319c430d3e24571d236d667fceba7","tid":404919,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"睇完某d po突然發神經想試下自己整望遠鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考慮過2種望遠鏡(折射同反射)<br />\n折射鏡: 設計簡單，鏡筒長，對鏡片要求高，有色散問題<br />\n反射鏡: 設計複雜，鏡筒短，對鏡片要求低，無色散問題<br />\n<br />\n因為無咩工具，預計整唔到d好精密既野<br />\n所以選擇折射鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預計分2階段<br />\n階段1: 出面隨便買放大鏡lens+紙皮鏡筒<br />\n階段2: 淘寶靚d既防色散lens+膠水管鏡筒<br />\n<br />\n設計:<br />\n前面係鏡片後面會接相機，有時間會再整個可以人眼望既後鏡<br />\n<br />\n階段1 參考e個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.savvyhomemade.com/building-a-homemade-telescope/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.savvyhomemade.com%2Fbuilding-a-homemade-telescope%2F&d=JCSSepq3pDacCyPCi12DSlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=d339a0a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.savvyhomemade.com/building-a-homemade-telescope/</a><br />\n<br />\n階段2 就e個<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/COrZaSm0LnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCOrZaSm0LnY&d=JCSSepq3pDacCyPCi12DSlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=714a8826\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/COrZaSm0LnY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾個問題要解決(歡迎一齊討論下):<br />\n1. 鏡身長度要點計?<br />\n2. 後面既相機用咩鏡對鏡身長度有無影響?<br />\n3. 要點固定塊鏡片?<br />\n4. 痴野用既膠水用邊種好? (本人diy白痴)<br />\n5. 諗到再問"},{"pid":"f60cb23679507ec05aac69f623e40198da55c197","tid":404919,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"望唔望到月球？"},{"pid":"646352037e390a6f02997536a9207f39de9d9d33","tid":404919,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>望唔望到月球？</blockquote><br />\n望到"},{"pid":"5fa0967b407683f734d9b4553a52d11d51232343","tid":404919,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"天文定手提嗰隻？"},{"pid":"31401cb3e0c0a7c1dc4f4a196fa3dc3e0dd767a8","tid":404919,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文定手提嗰隻？</blockquote><br />\n天文"},{"pid":"ee4f9ab3bed0ffa5e1ddfed390fe54ae5d877eb4","tid":404919,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天文定手提嗰隻？</blockquote><br />\n天文</blockquote><br />\n可以整隻細細地手提都ok"},{"pid":"7fc91755664e69297f9cff803fdaa07ac68e30dc","tid":404919,"uid":127770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"A4紙*1<br />\n膠紙*1cm<br />\n創意*0<br />\n圈成幼身圓柱體，貼張膠紙，完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91da4b407fd8f5e475ca266f6dec27d0ae17cf1","tid":404919,"uid":63080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/17/Galileantelescope_2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F17%2FGalileantelescope_2.png&h=3f7c9520&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5690114efa23e32ee79d8297ec9c6fbfa5e7a2cc","tid":404919,"uid":63080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"管長係凸鏡焦距減凹鏡焦距<br />\n所以效果好唔好就睇塊鏡既焦距準唔準<br />\n其中一個唔準都會失焦"},{"pid":"a30465891eb9899d8852361388981fa2fa6e3f2a","tid":404919,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>管長係凸鏡焦距減凹鏡焦距<br />\n所以效果好唔好就睇塊鏡既焦距準唔準<br />\n其中一個唔準都會失焦</blockquote><br />\n所以我整個鏡筒應該會2段式可以較一較d位"},{"pid":"b06b9931a1c740e0fa8407414af242d8736a7279","tid":404919,"uid":141892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"以前中學時有個同學都整過, 加油."}]}